lead_paragraph: South Africa lock Eben Etzebeth is unlikely to be fit to play against Wales in Cardiff on Saturday as his recovery from concussion proceeds slowly, coach Allister Coetzee said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: South Africa's Etzebeth Likely to Miss Wales Test
